<br>
If I'm there anyway and they need a res, free unless they want to donate.<br>
<br>
If I have to take 1 portal stone and res or zone in from PoK out of my way about 50-100pp sounds fair.<br>
<br>
If I have to run to WW or other way out of the way place and you're not a friend or guildie, cough up 500pp or get lost.<br>
<br>
KEI - I usually pay 35pp-50pp per character or sometimes depending on how broke I am (lately a lot, damn spells) 35pp for both.<br>
<br>
Virtue - You provide the dot and are standing there I usually do it for free. If I provide the dot usually 20pp or whatever your feel is fair beyond the dot cost.<br>
<br>
Summoning items - I personally hate waiting for people to show up for these. If you want items summoned be standing next to my mage ready for them. I usually just go off what people think is fair for this since they usually only want a damage bracer or spell haste item. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23503" target="top">Cerranshaun Lightbringer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
