<br>
If the tell recipient doesn't like that, and tells me; its good, I'm well aware that some folks value this stuff more than me.  Off I go to the next prospect.<br>
<br>
If the tell recipient could care less, then I get my buffs/whatever, they get a /bow and a /thank and off I go.<br>
<br>
It's only those rare times when they can't apparently read the english language, give me what I want, and then get all pissy that I'm not donating anything that causes issues.  In the end, they mark me down as an A$$hole, I mark them down as a clueless git, and we never talk to each other again.<br>
<br>
Its win/win/win baby. <p>Ninen of Saryrn<br>
