<br>
1-800-33MINTS is the number you call to order girl scout cookies from anywhere. <br>
<br>
Secondly, I very rarely get rezzes, usually because if I died it was probably my fault and I don't see the point in dragging innocent bystanders into my own stupidity. I don't die much though. At least on my main.<br>
<br>
As far as buffs and ports and all those other fun little things... I don't ask for them. If Im running through PoK and I see someone advertising buffy-services, I might go pick one up.. at the advertised price... Fair is fair. <br>
<br>
Pulling corpses? If Im not busy, and have some time to kill, Ill pull one for the price of a coffin, sometimes Ill pay for the coffin too. Why? Because Im nice maybe. Or because I remember the time my body was going to rot in less than a half hour and some necro was going to charge me 850pp to pull it out of a wall in HK. And the GMs were nowhere to be found. I was level 23, did not have 850pp, and was a little upset because Id already ran and bought the coffin and the necro was in zone. <br>
<br>
I don't mind compensating people for their time and/or mana, but there is a fine line between a business deal and exploitation. <br>
<br>
Um.. yeah. Stuff and things.<br>
